---
title: Teriyaki Chicken Meatballs with Stir-Fry Veggies and Garlic Rice
description: Get all the flavours of your fave Japanese takeout without the wait! Sweet and savoury teriyaki glazes chicken meatballs served with a prepped veggie mix and garlicky rice.
